Package: MMVbase
Type: Package
Title: Basic functions and coding patterns used across MMV R packages and scripting workflows
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(person("Venelin", "Mitov", email = "venelin.mitov@intiquan.com",
                    comment = '<a href="https://intiquan.com">IntiQuan AG</a>',
                    role = c("aut", "cre", "cph")))
Maintainer: Venelin Mitov <venelin.mitov@intiquan.com>
Description: Contains basic R functions which are not specific for any use case but 
  are general enough, so that they can be used in the implementation of modeling and
  simulation use cases more specific packages or workflow scripts. The package collects 
  such functions, together with documented coding examples and good practices.
